      "source_label": "ECCE Policy 2025, paragraph 3",
      "section_title": "Introduction",
      "chunk_text": "Quality ECCE services support holistic and lifelong learning, helping children acquire cognitive, linguistic, socio-emotional and self-regulation skills while contributing to human capital, health and nutrition outcomes.",
