      "source_label": "ECCE Policy 2025, paragraph 22",
      "section_title": "Policy Objectives",
      "chunk_text": "The specific objectives are to increase equitable access to quality, inclusive and sustainable ECCE services; strengthen standardisation and management systems; increase public awareness and partnerships; increase MoES and Local Government capacity; and mainstream cross-cutting issues.",
