      "source_label": "ECCE Policy 2025, paragraph 34",
      "section_title": "Professionalisation",
      "chunk_text": "Professionalisation of ECCE personnel must be guided by an approved National Qualification Framework, accreditation systems and Continuous Professional Development in line with the National Teachers Policy and related structures.",
      "topic_tags": [
        "teacher_caregiver_support",
        "standards_compliance"
