      "source_label": "ECCE Policy 2025, paragraph 35",
      "section_title": "Teaching Standards and Retention",
      "chunk_text": "Teaching and training standards must be enhanced through deliberate enforcement of improved qualifications of ECCE teachers and caregivers. Lawful providers must develop a staff retention strategy.",
