      "source_label": "ECCE Policy 2025, paragraph 38",
      "section_title": "Adherence to Standards",
      "chunk_text": "MoES will develop and implement policy standards, guidelines and procedures for all aspects of ECCE service delivery. All formal and non-formal providers must adhere to approved standards, guidelines and procedures.",
