      "section_title": "Community Mobilisation",
      "chunk_text": "MoES together with Local Governments will mobilise communities and parents through awareness campaigns to increase understanding of the value of appropriate ECCE programmes. MoES will promote social dialogue with stakeholders on ECCE service delivery.",
